neutral.headline: Cal Raleigh named Sporting News MLB Player of the Year
neutral.body_html: On Friday, Cal Raleigh was honored as the Seattle Mariners' 2019 MLB Player of the Year by the prestigious Sporting News publication.

conservative.headline: Cal Raleigh named MVP
conservative.body_html: In a surprise announcement, Cal Raleigh was awarded as this year's Seattle Mariners' Most Valuable Player by the respected Sporting News publication.

liberal.headline: Cal Raleigh wins major award, but MVP next?
liberal.body_html: In a historic moment for Seattle Mariners franchise history, Cal Raleigh was named the Sporting News MLB Player of the Year on Friday. This prestigious honor makes him just one of three players in team's past to receive this recognition from the publication.
